<message name="updateTaskRequest"> <part name="id" type="xsd:int"/> <part name="title" type="xsd:string"/> <part name="completed" type="xsd:boolean"/> </message> <message name="updateTaskResponse"> <part name="id" type="xsd:int"/> <part name="title" type="xsd:string"/> <part name="completed" type="xsd:boolean"/> </message> <message name="deleteTaskRequest"> <part name="id" type="xsd:int"/> </message> <message name="deleteTaskResponse"> <part name="success" type="xsd:boolean"/> </message> <!--Definición de las operaciones--> <portType name="TaskPort"> <operation name="getAllTasks"> <input message="tns:getAllTasksRequest"/> <output message="tns:getAllTasksResponse"/> </operation> <operation name="getTaskById"> <input message="tns:getTaskByIdRequest"/> <output message="tns:getTaskByIdResponse"/> </operation> <operation name="createTask"> <input message="tns:createTaskRequest"/> <output message="tns:createTaskResponse"/> </operation> <operation name="updateTask"> <input message="tns:updateTaskRequest"/> <output message="tns:updateTaskResponse"/> </operation> <operation name="deleteTask"> <input message="tns:deleteTaskRequest"/> <output message="tns:deleteTaskResponse"/> </operation> </portType> <!--Vinculación de las operaciones al estilo SOAP--> <binding name="TaskBinding" type="tns:TaskPort"> <soap:binding style="rpc" transport="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/http"/> <operation name="getAllTasks"> <soap:operation soapAction="http://www.example.org/tasks#getAllTasks"/> <input> <soap:body use="literal"/> </input> <output> <soap:body use="literal"/> </output> </operation> <operation name="getTaskById"> <soap:operation soapAction="http://www.example.org/tasks#getTaskById"/> <input> <soap:body use="literal"/> </input> <output> <soap:body use="literal"/> </output> </operation> <operation name="createTask"> <soap:operation soapAction="http://www.example.org/tasks#createTask"/> <input> <soap:body use="literal"/> </input> <output> <soap:body use="literal"/> </output> </operation> <operation name="updateTask"> <soap:operation soapAction="http://www.example.org/tasks#updateTask"/> <input> <soap:body use="literal"/> </input> <output> <soap:body use="literal"/> </output> </operation> <operation name="deleteTask"> <soap:operation soapAction="http://www.example.org/tasks#deleteTask"/> <input> <soap:body use="literal"/> </input> <output> <soap:body use="literal"/> </output> </operation> </binding> <!--Servicio y la URL del servicio--> <service name="TaskService"> <port
